  ('dietitian-moex-07580', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-101-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在肝細胞之粒線體內，酮體（ketone body）中之乙醯乙酸（acetoacetate）是經由下列何種方式合成？', '["由丙酮酸（pyruvic acid）經羧化反應（carboxylation）後產生", "由天門冬胺酸（aspartic acid）經轉胺作用（transamination）後產生", "由β-羥基-β-甲基戊二酸單醯輔A（β-hydroxy-β-methylglutaryl CoA）經裂解反應後產生", "由α-酮戊醯酸（α-ketoglutaric acid）經氧化脫羧作用（oxidative decarboxylation）後產生"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ca8a32319b8e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3a1bf1c1b455", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101110", "c": "105", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第2次醫事人員考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07581', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-101-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關葡萄糖在細胞內被磷酸化的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["葡萄糖被磷酸化後，可將多數葡萄糖留於細胞內，不易穿透細胞膜到細胞外", "肝臟細胞內葡萄糖濃度高時，己糖激（hexokinase）是主要磷酸化葡萄糖的酵素", "當葡萄糖-6-磷酸（glucose-6-phosphate）濃度高時，可抑制己糖激的活性", "肝臟細胞內磷酸化葡萄糖的葡糖激（glucokinase） 可被胰島素調控"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ca8a32319b8e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3a1bf1c1b455", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101110", "c": "105", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第2次醫事人員考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
